    "title": "Career Opportunity Financial Analyst at SIDBI",
    "description": "We at SIDBI are looking for an experienced Financial Analyst based out of Howrah. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout SIDBI:\nSIDBI is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Forecasting\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n• Proficiency in Budgeting\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Howrah, West Bengal, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with SIDBI!",
